1. tsc --init
2. npm init -y
3. Go to tsconfig file after creating the dist(index.js) and src folder(index.ts)
4. find outDir uncomment that and give the path
5. tsc -w   //watch
6. npm i lite-server
7. go to package.json and  under scripts give new name from test and and pass name "lite-server"
8. remember you add the js that inside the dist folder linked in html file
9. open new terminal also and tsc -w